# SignalForge Environment Variables

# Anthropic API key for LLM-powered analysis (Claude)
# Without this, detectors fall back to keyword matching
# Get yours at: https://console.anthropic.com/
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ScraperAPI key for bot-protected sites (Reddit, G2, Capterra, Google)
# Without this, review/job/pricing collectors are skipped
# Get yours at: https://www.scraperapi.com/
SCRAPER_API_KEY=...
